missionEventData.data1:
Ordnance and Supply Command has alerted Sector Command that one of our freighters has broken down in the Rudrig sector.
Your mission is to provide protection while one of our technical shuttles jumps in to repair the freighter. Ensure that both the freighter and the shuttle safely exit the system.
Beware that there are pirates active in this area, ensure that they don't interfere with this operation.
Red01 head to the jump point immediately, the repair shuttle is already enroute.
Shuttle Type DX9 and escort this is the Freighter Ars Opus, identify youselves and state your intention
Ars Opus, this is Alliance Shuttle Riker here to provide assistance.
Are we glad to see you! Some suspicious ships have started jumping in and out of the system. We we're starting to get worried.
Understood. Red01 scan the nav buoys to see if we can get more information on these visitors. We'll assist the Opus.
Okay. Processing the information now. According to the data two groups of three fighters and one transport just left the adjoining system.
Based on the average flight time the first group should be entering the system about... now
Warning! Three fighters and one shuttle exiting hyperspace. They're Pirates!
Red01, the Ars Opus is still getting ready to jump. Keep those bandits off us!
Warning another group of Pirates is exiting hyperspace. Keep them busy.
Well done Red 1. Once the Riker has disengaged, we're ready to jump.
Thanks for you help Red01. See you at the rendezvous.

missionEventData.data2: ESCORT THE ARS OPUS OUT OF THE SYSTEM
ESCORT THE ARS OPUS OUT OF THE SYSTEM
